ActYukon First Nations Self-Government Act
PrecisAuthority to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT with each of eight Yukon First Nation peoples in order to incorporate an increase into the gross expenditure formula set out in Annex A to their respective (Self-Government) FINANCIAL TRANSFER AGREEMENTS.
